<h3 id="about-www">About WWW.</h3>

<p>WWW. its a subdomain. Your domain is http://yourdomain.com/. If someone mistakenly decides to type the 3 extra â€œWWWâ€ , he will be redirected to the real domain http://yourdomain.com/ so you wont lose any visit. This is much better and easier, the â€œWWWâ€ do not mean anything.</p>

